            "textblock": "The purpose of the study is to evaluate the safety of Rifaximin or placebo in subjects with\n      severe hepatic impairment and Hepatic Encephalopathy."
        }, 
        "brief_title": "The Efficacy, Safety, And Pharmacokinetics Of Rifaximin In Subjects With Severe Hepatic Impairment And Hepatic Encephalopathy", 
